PLAYER HELP
PICK
You may pick fruits (and sometimes seeds) from plants. Simple ~CCOMpick <fruit/seed> from <plant>~CHLP. Fruits are edible. You may plant fruits or seeds in fertile ground to make a plant grow there.

A 'pick' is also a tool used when digging in mines or when constructing
certain types of buildings. They are easliy acquired but are prone to
breakage because of the sort of abuse they are often put through.

~CLABSee also: ~CREFplants, dig, tools~CHLP
